<item>
            <title>[LU-2053] Significant memory leak in new crypto code</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2053</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The new cryptoapi code introduced a memory allocation in cfs_crypto_hash_init for hdesc that&apos;s never freed anywhere other than on error path in cfs_crypto_hash_init itself.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
