                            <comment id="45807" author="green" created="Mon, 1 Oct 2012 12:20:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Right, I had the same wrong assumption as you.&lt;br/&gt;
Though my (very limited) testing with leak tracing enabled did not find anything else.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="45784" author="adilger" created="Sun, 30 Sep 2012 20:26:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Strangely, I thought that cfs_alloc() has memory leak tracing, but it seems this is only true of OBD_ALLOC().  That means there is a real possibility of other memory leaks existing that we do not know about.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
